title: Chapter 4324 - Chapter 4324: 4323 Heaven Origin Creation Embryo!
body:
Chapter 4324 - Chapter 4324: 4323 Heaven Origin Creation Embryo!

Chapter 4324: 4323 heaven origin creation embryo!

Translator: 549690339

In the trading center of Tongtian Avenue.

Wang Xian, who was strolling around in boredom, came to a fantastic restaurant.

The restaurant was built with a tree and emitted an alluring fragrance.

Wang Xian had not eaten for a long time. He entered the restaurant for no reason and ordered a table full of delicacies to taste one by one.

Soon, plates of delicacies were served.

The delicacies from other universes were indeed unique.

The business of fantasy restaurant was also very good. It was always full of people.

Wang Xian ate the delicacies while sizing up his surroundings.

The customers around him were all masters in the mastery realm.

He even saw a master who had just entered the Heaven’s origin realm. He was hiding his aura and drinking there!

Wang Xian took a glance at the elder who had just entered the Heaven’s origin realm. A smile appeared on his face.

The elder sensed Wang Xian’s gaze and swept his gaze over.

However, he did not notice anything unusual.

He did not pay much attention to a disciple with the fire attribute who was at the peak of the Dominator realm.

“Such a situation is really dazzling!”

Wang Xian thought to himself.

There were as many disciples at the Dominator realm as dogs. It was common to meet strong people at the Heaven’s origin level.

They would even hide among the ordinary disciples and play with their lives.

“Eh?”

At this moment, a few young men and women with sharp swords walked into the restaurant.

Wang Xian’s gaze swept across them and landed on the young men and women. He felt a familiar aura.

“There’s an aura of the Heaven’s origin sword technique.”

Wang Xian looked at these young men and women and muttered.

The Heaven’s origin sword technique was a powerful sword technique that Wang Xian had obtained by accident.

It was a sword technique that could lead straight to the Heaven’s origin realm.

And this sword technique originated from the sword universe.

Wang Xian was not familiar with the sword universe. In fact, he only understood it from the Heaven’s origin sword technique.

But now, he could actually feel a familiar aura.

This Is?

A disciple of the universe of Swords?

“HMM?”

When he landed on the body of a woman in the middle, he raised his eyebrows slightly.

It was a little strange.

The woman was a sword cultivator with the darkness attribute. Her strength was at the eighth level of the ruler of the universe.

This was not what surprised Wang Xian.

What surprised him was that there seemed to be something in his body.

This thing contained an extremely powerful energy.

However, this thing was well hidden. If it wasn’t for the chaotic energy in Wang Xian’s body, he wouldn’t have been able to sense it.

“Not simple. It can actually block my detection.”

Wang Xian sensed for a moment but didn’t discover what this thing was. A look of astonishment appeared on his face.

One had to know that he was only a few dozen meters away from the lady. At such a close distance, he was actually unable to see through anything.

One could imagine that this thing was not simple.

It was at least an existence at the Heaven’s origin level.

“It’s a living thing!”

Wang Xian continued to think to himself.

Many guesses appeared in his mind.

“My Friend, you don’t have anyone here, right?”

At this moment, coincidentally, a few young men and women glanced around and came to Wang Xian’s side. They spoke to him.

“Sure!”

Wang Xian looked at them and nodded with a smile.

The six of them smiled and sat at the side.

When Wang Xian saw the woman approaching, he sensed her silently once again.

He looked at the woman and hesitated for a moment. Then, he said directly, “My friend, you have something dirty on you.”

“HMM?”

When the young men and women who had just sat down heard Wang Xian’s sudden words, they were stunned.

Jian Tian Yao, in particular, looked at Wang Xian in astonishment.

She sized up Wang Xian?

What was going on?

Was he trying to hit on her?

“Friend, what business do you have?”

Beside Jian Tian Yao, a young man frowned as he looked at Wang Xian and asked.

“I can feel an energy that doesn’t belong to me from her body. It’s very special.”

Wang Xian spoke and looked at Jian tianyao. “Can I sense it?”

“How can there be any energy that doesn’t belong to me? Are you mistaken?”

Jian Tianyao looked at Wang Xian in astonishment and frowned as well.

“I’m stronger than you, so I can sense it. Let me check it out.”

Wang Xian continued to speak to her.

Jian Tian Yao looked at Wang Xian and then at her companions.

“What do you want to see?”

Her senior brother beside her felt a sense of wariness as he looked at Wang Xian.

“Just use your energy to check it out!”

As Wang Xian spoke, a wisp of flame floated in front of Jian Tian Yao!

“Even my seniors didn’t sense anything special in my body. How can you sense it?”

Jian Tianyao didn’t believe this man who said that there was something strange in her body when they first met. She continued to ask cautiously.

“I have a special feeling. I just need to touch it and I will know.”

Wang Xian looked at her and continued.

He was prepared to make a move if this woman didn’t agree to it.

With his strength, she wouldn’t be able to sense him even if he made a move.

“I want to see what you are up to.”

Jian tianyao stared at the Wisp of flame in front of her and said!

“Don’t worry, I have no ill intentions!”

Wang Xian looked at him with a smile on his face. A wisp of flame landed on her body.

At this moment, the power of the flame entered Jian Tianyao’s body instantly.

Before she could react, Wang Xian had already sensed the energy in the ball.

“This is?”

Wang Xian’s face revealed a hint of surprise.

When his energy sensed the special thing in the woman’s body, he was a little shocked.

There was actually an existence at the level of Tianyuan creation in her body.

No, it couldn’t be said to be a powerhouse at the level of Tianyuan creation.

It was more like an existence at the level of Tianyuan creation was being nurtured in his body.

It was slightly different from the birth of Tianci by Tianci’s mother.

The Heaven’s origin creation in the woman’s body was a living being and not a treasure of the Heaven’s origin creation.

However, this living being was currently in a state of deep sleep and was extremely weak.

It had completely fused with the woman and was absorbing energy to revive.

“Possession? Or what is the situation?”

Wang Xian’s eyes were shining.

He wanted to capture it, but he realized that he could not capture it at all. It was as if he had completely fused with the woman.

Buzz

Wang Xian’s mind moved and mobilized the chaotic energy in his body.

That Thing was located in the woman’s body. It was as if Wang Xian had fused with the primal chaos stone.

It was extremely strange.

However, when Wang Xian mobilized that weak chaotic energy, he was able to capture that heaven origin blessed embryo.

His gaze focused.

Following that, on Jian Tian Yao’s body, a palm-sized, baby-like object was pulled out by Wang Xian.

When Jian Tian Yao saw an object coming out of her body, her face revealed a look of shock.

The faces of the few companions beside her changed slightly as well. They stood up immediately and stared at the strange embryo and Wang Xian vigilantly.
